    <label>Atom's Judgement</label>
    <description>"When you need to not just smash a problem, but wipe it off the face of the earth along with three neighboring blocks!"
This revolutionary tool combines:
The finesse of a surgical instrument (if the surgeon is a super mutant with PMS)
Eco-friendliness (radioactive contamination is just a free way to sterilize the area!)
Cost-effectiveness (every hit saves your ammo... and potentially - future heating bills!)
Design features:
A hammer made from 12 damaged Fusion Core nuclear batteries
Lead handle (absorbs 0.0001% of radiation)
Built-in Geiger counter (shows "OH" instead of numbers)
IMPORTANT:
After 10+ consecutive hits, the hammer automatically activates:
"Nuclear Hammer" mode (additional damage + glowing skin for 2 weeks)
"Mad Max" protocol (all car alarms within a mile are activated)
"Final Argument" function (turns user into a crater)
"Vault-Tec is not responsible for:
Sudden greening of the area (dark blue)
Unintentional creation of new species of fauna
Disappearance of small towns within a 5 km radius
Consult your radiologist before use!"</description>
